This will help you accelerate image load times easily with just a few clicks.
It works by replacing all image links from the web page currently loaded in your browser using a smart caching proxy, so multiple requests to the same image will load faster because it's already cached.

Note that you may want to disable it if it breaks images for certain websites.

What's new?
